  <div class="container clearfix text-center vacuum-forming-head">
    <h1>What is vacuum forming?</h1>
    <p class="text-left vacuum-forming-head-para">
      Vacuum forming is an upgraded version of the thermoforming technology 
      for forming materials in production. During the vacuum forming process, 
      the product is completely wrapped by particular films, 
      which are then placed within a mold and subject to extremely high 
      temperatures and pressures. This makes sure that the product is preciselyformed 
      to the exact required size.
    </p>
  </div>
